description:
The finale of Single's Inferno: Season 5 is scheduled to release on Netflix on February 10, 2026. 

This market will resolve to "Yes" if the listed participant successfully makes a final pair and leaves the island with their chosen match by the end of the final episode of Single's Inferno: Season 5. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No". 

Only the final pairs count; trips to Paradise will not qualify towards the resolution of this market. Only final choices count; initial preferences will have no effect on the resolution of this market. If the final episode of Single's Inferno: Season 5 does not air by February 28, 2026, 11:59PM ET, this market will resolve to "No".

The resolution source for this market will be the Netflix broadcast of the final episode of Single's Inferno: Season 5.
